<p><small>*Time period: January 2018 to December 2018, or from the time GrabFood was launched.</small></p>

<p>What’s driving this growth is not just die-hard bubble tea fans who can’t go a week without drinking this sweet treat, but a growing bubble tea fan club in Southeast Asia. The number of bubble tea lovers on GrabFood grew over 12,000% in 2018 - and there’s no sign of stopping!</p>

<p>With increasing consumer demand, how is Southeast Asia’s bubble tea supply catching up?  As of December 2018, GrabFood has close to 4,000 bubble tea outlets from a network of over 1,500 brands - a 200% growth in bubble tea outlets in Southeast Asia!</p>

