<h2 id="best-time-for-bubble-tea">Best Time for Bubble Tea!</h2>

<p>Don’t we all need a cup of sweet Bubble Tea in the afternoon to get us through the day?  Across Southeast Asia, GrabFood’s data reveals that most people order bubble tea to accompany their meals at lunch, or as a  perfect midday energiser!</p>

